Powers.DescLong: You have been raked by a claw.
The Disruptor Blast is continuing to damage you.
The Disruptor Tesla is holding you helpless.
Arachnobots can jump very high and travel very fast.

Armor plating gives Arachnobot Disrupter some resistance to smashing and lethal damage. They are generally well insulated to resist energy damage and EMP attacks. As machines, they are very resistant to psionic damage.  Arachnobots are good jumpers and are very fast.
You have been caught in a web.  You cannot move or fly and your attack speed is reduced.
